# ARPG — apps/kbve/astro-kbve isometric ARPG game art (sprites + ground)
# Pointer files live in this repo; blobs live on git.kbve.com/KBVE/arpg.git
# (see apps/kbve/astro-kbve/public/assets/arcade/arpg/.lfsconfig). Push/pull the
# blobs to the arpg endpoint with `./kbve.sh -lfs arpg <push|pull|...>`; the
# repo-root .lfsconfig still defaults to rareicon, so the wrapper injects the
# arpg endpoint. Raw 720px source sheets stay gitignored (characters/**/raw/).
apps/kbve/astro-kbve/public/assets/arcade/arpg/**/*.png filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
